# 409A evidence — generated outputs from `make valuation-evidence`
# These are regenerable on any commit; don't version-control noise.
# Appraiser-submission packs go in valuation/evidence-packs/ (committed).
# Ignore dated subdirs under valuation/evidence/ (regenerable detail) but
# allow .md files directly at valuation/evidence/ root (data-room index).
valuation/evidence/*/
valuation/algorithms/3a/
valuation/algorithms/3b/
valuation/algorithms/3c/
valuation/algorithms/3d/
